    c "Então, esbarramos em outro projeto de eugenia."

# game/episode022.rpy:277
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c3cfad89:

    # na "It seems so."
    na "É o que parece."

# game/episode022.rpy:278
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_8da960f6:

    # c "Can’t deny I’m a little disappointed."
    c "Não posso negar que estou um pouco decepcionado."

# game/episode022.rpy:279
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_4e435425:

    # c "Yet another bunch of sadistic aliens with a god-complex, murdering innocents to enhance themselves."
    c "Mais um grupo de alienígenas sadísticos que se acham deuses, matando inocentes para melhorar eles mesmos."

# game/episode022.rpy:281
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_74ff7e59:

    # na "It’s an age-old practice, unfortunately."
    na "Infelizmente, isso é uma prática muito antiga."

# game/episode022.rpy:282
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_45049574:

    # na "I’m not sure how successful this civilization on Petrarch was, to be honest, I’ve never heard of this transfusion process."
    na "Sinceramente, não sei quanto o quão bem-sucedida espécie foi essa civilização em Petrarch. Nunca ouvi falar nesse processo de conclusão."

# game/episode022.rpy:284
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_3b4b55fb:

    # "Our attention was drawn to the scientist and the subject on the table again."
    "Nossa atenção voltou para a cientista e a sujeita na mesa."

# game/episode022.rpy:285
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c730b52a:

    # shk "The transfusion is complete, Your Majesty."
    shk "A transfusão está completa, Vossa Majestade."

# game/episode022.rpy:287
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_cbbddb51:

    # th "Wish he’d drop the whole “Your Majesty” crap."
    th "Queria que ela parasse com essa merda de “Vossa Majestade”."

# game/episode022.rpy:289
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_60979edf:

    # c "He’d probably lose his head if he didn’t use those honorifics."
    c "Acho que cortariam a cabeça dela fora se ele não usasse isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:290
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_1b5528fb:

    # na "From what we’ve heard so far of them, I don’t think they’re a very forgiving kind of people."
    na "Pelo que vimos até agora, acho que não são um povo muito piedoso."

# game/episode022.rpy:292
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_212b4acf:

    # shk "Allow the test subject to demonstrate the newly transfused abilities."
    shk "Permita que a sujeita demonstre suas novas habilidades."

# game/episode022.rpy:293
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_42d2e38d:

    # shk "The transfusion has strengthened the mind of the subject as is about to become clear."
    shk "A transfusão fortaleceu a mente da sujeita, como ficará claro agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:295
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_54b73645:

    # "The view switched to the test subject looking at a metallic object."
    "A visão mudou para a sujeita olhando para um objeto metálico."

# game/episode022.rpy:297
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_ef757bf5:

    # "The alien appeared to be concentrating very hard on the object and we waited for something to happen."
    "A alienígena parecia estar bem concentrada no objeto, e esperamos algo acontecer."

# game/episode022.rpy:309
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b7102d52:

    # "Slowly, but surely, the object began to rise from the tabletop, until it hovered a few inches above it."
    "O objeto começou a subir lentamente da mesa, até flutuar alguns centímetros acima."

# game/episode022.rpy:310
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d8bd1d6b:

    # c "Woah, he’s making it float with his mind?"
    c "Eita, ela fez aquilo flutuar com a mente?"

# game/episode022.rpy:312
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c3cfad89_1:

    # na "It seems so."
    na "Parece que sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:314
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_38e4fbf5:

    # th "That has to be some kind of trick."
    th "Deve ser algum truque."

# game/episode022.rpy:315
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_e607735f:

    # c "Unlikely, lying to a king would be unwise, especially with the threat of beheadings and all."
    c "Eu não acho provável. Não seria muito esperto mentir agora, ainda mais podendo perder a cabeça."

# game/episode022.rpy:317
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_40cbd290:

    # shk "The test subject has fully incorporated the mental capabilities of the lesser species and is another step toward full enlightenment."
    shk "A sujeita incorporou completamente as habilidades mentais da espécie inferior, e está um passo mais perto da total iluminação."

# game/episode022.rpy:318
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_008790b9:

    # c "A little ironic calling all the other aliens lesser beings, but stealing their special characteristics to use on yourself."
    c "Irônico chamarem as outras raças de inferiores, só para roubar as características especiais delas."

# game/episode022.rpy:320
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_de66f6f5:

    # "Another scientist approached the one currently speaking to us."
    "Outra cientista se aproximou da que estava falando."

# game/episode022.rpy:321
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_8f545a82:

    # shk "I told you not to disturb us."
    shk "Eu falei para não nos incomodar."

# game/episode022.rpy:322
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_71c62419:

    # man2 "I’m sorry, sir, but there’s been a security incident."
    man2 "Desculpe senhora, mas houve um problema na segurança."

# game/episode022.rpy:323
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_04fe8219:

    # shk "An incident?"
    shk "Um problema?"

# game/episode022.rpy:324
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_09e76e55:

    # shk "Why has the alarm not sounded?"
    shk "Porque não soaram o alarme?"

# game/episode022.rpy:326
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_82f5e810:

    # "As if on queue, a great many sirens began to blare."
    "Como se fosse na deixa, várias sirenes começaram a berrar."

# game/episode022.rpy:327
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_06452061:

    # man2 "There’s an invasion force at our doorstep, sir."
    man2 "Tem uma força invasora na nossa porta, senhora."

# game/episode022.rpy:328
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b573abbb:

    # shk "Impossible!"
    shk "Impossível!"

# game/episode022.rpy:329
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b5578ee8:

    # man2 "They came out of nowhere."
    man2 "Eles apareceram do nada."

# game/episode022.rpy:331
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_9882abdc:

    # shk "Which breed of mongrels have dared to defy us?"
    shk "Que raça inferior ousou nos desafiar?"

# game/episode022.rpy:332
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_bc6b436b:

    # man2 "It’s an alliance of the lesser races, sir."
    man2 "É uma aliança de raças inferiores, senhora."

# game/episode022.rpy:333
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_1556eb04:

    # man2 "They’ve come to put a stop to us."
    man2 "Eles vieram nos impedir."

# game/episode022.rpy:334
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d7cfcdd9:

    # man2 "Bombardments have already started."
    man2 "Começaram os bombardeios."

# game/episode022.rpy:336
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f8026d6b:

    # shk "They will never destroy us."
    shk "Eles nunca vão nos destruir."

# game/episode022.rpy:337
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_2534e603:

    # shk "Keep filming, we’ll record their defeat for the enjoyment of the future generations of our glorious race."
    shk "Continue filmando, vamos registrar a derrota deles para o deleite de gerações futuras da nossa raça gloriosa."

# game/episode022.rpy:338
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_bef08778:

    # c "I guess they’re finally getting their just reward."
    c "Acho que finalmente vão ter que merecem."

# game/episode022.rpy:340
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_0431e39e:

    # "The simulation pixellated again and now we were standing outside, overlooking the field outside the temple."
    "A simulação ficou pixelada novamente, e agora estamos fora, olhando para um campo fora do tempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:341
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_53757911:

    # "Several soldiers were holding the scientists at gunpoint."
    "Haviam vários soldados apontando armas para as cientistas."

# game/episode022.rpy:344
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b92db381:

    # man "Your reign of terror ends here, Shixses scum."
    man "O seu reino de terror acaba aqui, lixo Shixses."

# game/episode022.rpy:347
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_66597e2e:

    # shk "You think you can defeat us?"
    shk "Vocês acham que podem nos derrotar?"

# game/episode022.rpy:348
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_0aaec02a:

    # shk "We are your masters in everything!"
    shk "Somos suas mestres em tudo!"

# game/episode022.rpy:350
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d8d38a89:

    # man "Not for long."
    man "Não por muito tempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:351
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c61c757f:

    # man "The plague will kill you soon enough."
    man "A praga vai logo matar vocês."

# game/episode022.rpy:353
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_9092e245:

    # shk "Fool, we are immune to the diseases you weaklings contract."
    shk "Tolo, somos imunes às doenças que seres fracos como vocês contraem."

# game/episode022.rpy:355
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_3dbd2677:

    # man "That may be true."
    man "Isso pode até ser verdade."

# game/episode022.rpy:356
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_a9ab7767:

    # man "But the bio-engineered virus we’re about to release is sure to kill you."
    man "Mas o vírus criado no laboratório que vamos soltar com certeza vai matar vocês."

# game/episode022.rpy:357
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_933bfc24:

    # man "Believe me, the test subjects of your supposed master race begged to be killed when they slowly perished."
    man "Acredite, as cobaias da sua suposta raça superior imploraram pela morte enquanto morriam lentamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:359
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_06e3eccf:

    # shk "Lies."
    shk "Mentira."

# game/episode022.rpy:361
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_34221d12:

    # man "You’ll find out soon enough."
    man "Você já vai descobrir."

# game/episode022.rpy:362
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_bb6f0956:

    # man "Now move aside and give us access to your laboratory."
    man "Agora saia da frente e nos dê acesso ao seu laboratório."

# game/episode022.rpy:364
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f8fb3476:

    # shk "I would never give a mongrel like you access to our life’s work, even if I could."
    shk "Eu nunca daria acesso ao trabalho da nossa vida inteira a um vira-lata que nem você, nem que pudesse."

# game/episode022.rpy:366
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_5df0672a:

    # man "What do you mean?"
    man "Como assim?"

# game/episode022.rpy:367
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_4258e90d:

    # shk "The laboratory, like any of the other labs on Petrarch, has been sealed as soon as the third-stage alarm sounded."
    shk "O laboratório, como qualquer outro em Petrarch, foi selado assim que soou o alarme de terceiro estágio."

# game/episode022.rpy:368
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_641b224b:

    # shk "You’ll never gain entry."
    shk "Vocês nunca vão conseguir entrar."

# game/episode022.rpy:369
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_6b2090c9:

    # shk "Even we no longer have access."
    shk "Nem nós temos acesso agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:371
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d708d801:

    # "The soldier appeared fazed by this statement and conferred with his squad."
    "O soldado parecia chocado com isso, e foi consultar se o esquadrão."

# game/episode022.rpy:372
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_6aab6da1:

    # man "I guess we’ll just have to nuke the place."
    man "Então o jeito é jogar uma bomba nuclear."

# game/episode022.rpy:374
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f969b5a2:

    # man2 "Sir, I’ve just had reports from elsewhere on Petrarch."
    man2 "Senhor,  acabei de receber relatórios de outro lugar em Petrarch."

# game/episode022.rpy:375
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_5088bdd9:

    # man2 "Several nuclear detonations have executed and all of the labs still stand."
    man2 "Várias detonações nucleares foram executadas e todos os laboratórios ainda estão de pé."

# game/episode022.rpy:376
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_592d08eb:

    # man "Impossible!"
    man "Impossível!"

# game/episode022.rpy:378
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f03c50bf:

    # "The Shixses scientist began to laugh manically."
    "A cientista Shixses começou a gargalhar loucamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:379
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c4b11fec:

    # man "I guess we have to let the gas do its work then."
    man "Então vamos ter que deixar o gás cuidar disso."

# game/episode022.rpy:380
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_eb2a4837:

    # man "Laugh all you want because of your small triumph, but you’ll wish I’d shot you in the head soon enough."
    man "Pode rir o quanto quiser com esse seu pequeno triunfo, logo logo você vai querer ter levado bala na cabeça."

# game/episode022.rpy:382
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_1bc3ebfe:

    # "With those word, the squadron of soldiers left."
    "Com essas palavras, o esquadrão saiu."

# game/episode022.rpy:384
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_733d252d:

    # "The simulation skipped to another moment ahead in time."
    "A simulação pulou mais à frente."

# game/episode022.rpy:385
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_0119655f:

    # "Great noxious-looking clouds billowed over the field in front of the temple, now strewn with the bodies of many Shixses."
    "Grandes nuvens tóxicas se espalhavam pelo campo em frente ao templo, que agora estava cheio dos copos de várias Shixses."

# game/episode022.rpy:386
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_5398f068:

    # "Screams and rattling cries of death filled the air."
    "O ar estava cheio de gritos e sons de morte."

# game/episode022.rpy:387
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_fddfbccd:

    # "The scientist who’d spoken to the soldiers collapsed on the ground, clutching his chest."
    "A cientista que havia falado com os soldados estava caído no chão, apertando o peito."

# game/episode022.rpy:388
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_3886a6e9:

    # "The angle of the recording skewed weirdly as well and we found ourselves level with the floor."
    "O ângulo da gravação ficou todo torto, e ficamos na altura do chão."

# game/episode022.rpy:390
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_a7eaf842:

    # shk "This...{w} This is the end."
    shk "Esse...{w} Esse é o fim."

# game/episode022.rpy:391
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d37eee7f:

    # shk "The lesser races have committed genocide."
    shk "As raças inferiores cometeram genocídio."

# game/episode022.rpy:392
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_fa910473:

    # shk "I’m...{w} I’m afraid you’ll never see this recording of our glorious work, Your Majesty."
    shk "Eu...{w} sinto que nunca poderá ver esta gravação do nosso glorioso trabalho, Vossa Majestade."

# game/episode022.rpy:393
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_9e0e2831:

    # shk "But know that contingencies are in place."
    shk "Mas saiba que temos planos de contingência."

# game/episode022.rpy:394
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_3150fb5d:

    # shk "We’ve spread a cryptic record of our accomplishments in a great many systems across the galaxy."
    shk "Espalhamos gravações de nossas conquistas em vários sistemas pela galáxia."

# game/episode022.rpy:395
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_ec73fbf7:

    # shk "A prophecy that’s bound to attract attention from curious minds, ripe for their own journey toward enlightenment."
    shk "Uma profecia que deve atrair a atenção de várias mentes curiosas, prontas para sua própria jornada a caminho da iluminação."

# game/episode022.rpy:396
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_a78c5d2a:

    # shk "Even if we’re completely wiped out by those treacherous weaklings we were supposed to rule over."
    shk "Mesmo se formos completamente exterminadas por aqueles fracos que devíamos ter dominado."

# game/episode022.rpy:397
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b21acd8a:

    # shk "Another species will pick up our mantle and continue our great endeavor."
    shk "Outra espécie tomará nosso lugar e continuar a nossa grande jornada."

# game/episode022.rpy:398
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_206a5d1f:

    # shk "Our temples will unlock themselves again on their arrival, bestowing our knowledge."
    shk "Nossos tempos se abrirão novamente com a sua chegada, concedendo nosso conhecimento."

# game/episode022.rpy:399
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_be0a1ef8:

    # shk "They will better themselves and erect a glorious monument in our memory."
    shk "Eles se aperfeiçoarão e construirão um grande monumento em nossa memória."

# game/episode022.rpy:400
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_aa3d9454:

    # shk "The end...{w} It comes..."
    shk "O fim...{w} Ele vem..."

# game/episode022.rpy:401
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_9a93ab3a:

    # shk "It cleanses!"
    shk "Ele limpa!"

# game/episode022.rpy:403
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_4f9503e4:

    # shk "It cl...{w} ean...{w} s...{w} es..."
    shk "El...{w} e...{w} lim...{w} pa..."

# game/episode022.rpy:408
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f9493663:

    # "The simulation cut out at this point and we were back in the temple."
    "A simulação termina nesse momento, e estávamos de volta ao templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:409
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d12fa3f5:

    # th "Fuck."
    th "Caralho."

# game/episode022.rpy:410
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_fbe261dd:

    # th "I really didn’t need to see all that."
    th "Eu não precisava ter visto isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:411
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_ac2bea30:

    # c "Me neither."
    c "Nem eu."

# game/episode022.rpy:412
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_335795f6:

    # c "Though it did make some things a lot clearer."
    c "Mas esclareceu umas coisas."

# game/episode022.rpy:413
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b7671da0:

    # c "Those Shixses spread the Prophecy to lure people here."
    c "Aquelas Shixses espalharam a profecia para atrair pessoas."

# game/episode022.rpy:415
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c756ce9b:

    # c "Have you ever heard about a genocide on Petrarch, mom?"
    c "Mãe, já ouviu falar de algum genocídio em Petrarch?"

# game/episode022.rpy:417
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_a1e0a36f:

    # c "Have you ever heard about a genocide on Petrarch, Nadya?"
    c "Nadya, já ouviu falar de algum genocídio em Petrarch?"

# game/episode022.rpy:419
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d8763a46:

    # na "I’ve never even heard of Petrarch before, nor of the Shixses or a genocide by a targeted virus."
    na "Nunca tinha nem ouvido falar de Petrarch, nem de Shixses, ou de algum genocídio usando vírus direcionado."

# game/episode022.rpy:420
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_2d9c8828:

    # na "Their eradication must have been complete, all records were scrubbed."
    na "Devem ter sido completamente erradicadas, todos os registros destruídos."

# game/episode022.rpy:422
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d7ae0fa8:

    # th "Except for the simulation we’ve just witnessed and the databanks supposedly waiting to be unlocked."
    th "Tirando a simulação que vimos, e os bancos de dados que estão esperando serem abertos."

# game/episode022.rpy:423
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_5b970f84:

    # c "I’m fairly certain we unlocked those temples."
    c "Tenho quase certeza que a gente abriu esse templos."

# game/episode022.rpy:424
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_74cfca1a:

    # c "Were we scanned when we set foot on Petrarch?"
    c "Escanearam a gente quando descemos em Petrarch?"

# game/episode022.rpy:426
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_5bef2cca:

    # th "I don’t know, it could be?"
    th "Não sei, talvez?"

# game/episode022.rpy:427
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_9825b369:

    # c "The Shixses were hoping for someone to inherit their research."
    c "As Shixses estavam esperando que alguém fosse herdar sua pesquisa."

# game/episode022.rpy:428
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_72fecd39:

    # c "I sure as hell don’t want anything to do with that eugenics program they were running."
    c "Eu que não quero ter nada a ver com esse projeto de eugenia que elas estavam fazendo."

# game/episode022.rpy:430
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_d828b031:

    # na "Me neither, but Agust wants to."
    na "Nem eu, mas Agust quer."

# game/episode022.rpy:432
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_2cf8adcd:

    # th "And I guess the Confessor craves for a chance to do some of those magic tricks of his for real."
    th "E parece que o Confessor quer a chance de fazer alguns daqueles truques de mágica dele de verdade."

# game/episode022.rpy:433
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f996682b:

    # th "I mean we all saw that test subject levitate an object with its mind."
    th "Bem, acho que todo mundo aqui viu a sujeita de testes levitar um objeto com a mente."

# game/episode022.rpy:434
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_815e38f8:

    # c "Yes, I guess something like that would elevate his parlor tricks."
    c "Sim, acho que algo assim melhoraria os truques de mágica dele."

# game/episode022.rpy:435
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_b75b694d:

    # c "I think it’s clear what we need to do."
    c "Bom, ficou bem claro o que temos que fazer."

# game/episode022.rpy:436
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_72bafa3e:

    # c "We need to blow up this place as soon as possible."
    c "Temos que explodir esse lugar assim que possível."

# game/episode022.rpy:438
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_1f573468:

    # na "But how?"
    na "Mas como?"

# game/episode022.rpy:439
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_25aef142:

    # na "Nuclear explosions supposedly didn’t make a dent in those buildings."
    na "Parece que nem explosões nucleares conseguiram arranhar esses prédios."

# game/episode022.rpy:440
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_33755c1b:

    # c "True, but we have access to the interior of those buildings."
    c "Verdade, mas temos acesso ao interior desses prédios."

# game/episode022.rpy:441
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_1a95398e:

    # c "Thyia, do you think you can rig something to get it to explode inside?"
    c "Thyia, acha que consegue fazer alguma coisa explodir por dentro?"

# game/episode022.rpy:443
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_c79bbcd0:

    # th "Yes, we have some supplies on the Bastard and there’s enough lying around inside the compound to build something."
    th "Sim, temos uns suplementos na Bastarda, e tem o bastante dentro do lugar para construir alguma coisa."

# game/episode022.rpy:444
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_995847df:

    # c "Good, we’ll start with this temple here and work our way through the remaining buildings."
    c "Ótimo, vamos começar com esse templo aqui e daí ver os outros prédios."

# game/episode022.rpy:446
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_a79487b1:

    # na "That’s going to take a while."
    na "Isso vai demorar um pouco."

# game/episode022.rpy:447
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_f7400097:

    # c "I don’t care."
    c "Não importa."

# game/episode022.rpy:448
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_dc1cfa50:

    # c "This research should never fall into my father’s hands, or anyone, for that matter."
    c "Essa pesquisa não deve cair nas mãos do meu pai, nem de ninguém."

# game/episode022.rpy:450
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_e4268d37:

    # th "No argument there."
    th "Concordo."

# game/episode022.rpy:451
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_93837ad5:

    # th "Let’s head back so we can start working on those explosives."
    th "Vamos voltar e ver essa questão dos explosivos."

# game/episode022.rpy:465
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_203b710f:

    # "Céline took us back to the compound where we brought everyone up to speed with what we just learned."
    "Céline nos levou de volta ao complexo, e informamos o pessoal sobre o que acabamos de descobrir."

# game/episode022.rpy:466
translate portuguese ep022_temple_simulation_bc8a95de:

    # "Thyia and Jade told everyone what sort of tech to gather in order to make the required bombs."
    "Thyia e Jade avisaram ao pessoal qual o tipo de tecnologia pegar para fazer as bombas."

# game/episode022.rpy:513
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_700ee8a8:

    # "Eva was pulling cables out of the wall when I found her."
    "Eva estava puxando cabos da parede quando encontrei ela."

# game/episode022.rpy:514
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_14185f68:

    # c "Seems like you enjoy ripping out that shit."
    c "Parece que você adora arrancar essa merda aí."

# game/episode022.rpy:515
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_62698661:

    # e "Gives me something to vent my frustration."
    e "É uma forma de descontar a minha raiva."

# game/episode022.rpy:516
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_3fc15ae0:

    # c "Are you okay?"
    c "Tudo bem com você?"

# game/episode022.rpy:518
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_e2cae267:

    # e "I’m just glad I didn’t have to watch that simulation you saw."
    e "Só fico feliz que não tive que ver essa simulação que vocês viram."

# game/episode022.rpy:519
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_4f532b10:

    # e "How could they do something like that?"
    e "Como que puderam fazer algo assim?"

# game/episode022.rpy:520
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_f9eaba3a:

    # c "Harvest other species, you mean?"
    c "Fazer o quê, roubar das outras espécies?"

# game/episode022.rpy:522
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_118adec5:

    # e "Yes."
    e "Sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:523
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_0cad46cd:

    # c "They were pretty full of themselves, so I guess at some point they didn’t view other beings as real living things anymore."
    c "Elas eram bem arrogantes, acho que a certa altura simplesmente não viam mais outras criaturas como seres vivos."

# game/episode022.rpy:525
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_dd475dda:

    # e "And we unlocked all that again."
    e "E nós acordamos isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:526
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_46c3a7e1:

    # c "We did, but we’re also going to bury it for good again."
    c "Sim, mas também vamos acabar de vez com isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:527
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_5cdee39e:

    # e "Will it work, blowing up that temple, I mean?"
    e "Vai dar certo? Explodir o templo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:528
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_fa728664:

    # c "Thyia is pretty confident it will."
    c "A Thyia está bem certa que sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:529
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_240c6e48:

    # c "Then we’re going to move onto the other buildings, make sure nothing remains."
    c "Aí vamos fazer o mesmo com os outros prédios, garantir que não vai ficar nada de pé."

# game/episode022.rpy:531
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_c4b301f6:

    # e "Good, I want it all to burn."
    e "Ótimo, quero que queime tudo."

# game/episode022.rpy:532
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_20c70dc1:

    # c "That’s the plan."
    c "Essa é a ideia."

# game/episode022.rpy:534
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_e8bba641:

    # e "This is what dad and all those other people are after, isn’t it?"
    e "Isso é o que o pai e aquele monte de gente estão atrás, né?"

# game/episode022.rpy:536
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_e8f46d4d:

    # e "This is what your dad and all those other people are after, isn’t it?"
    e "Isso é o que o seu pai e aquele monte de gente estão atrás, né?"

# game/episode022.rpy:537
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_058dd7b5:

    # c "Yes, I think so."
    c "Sim, acho que é."

# game/episode022.rpy:539
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_ccb4f47a:

    # c "It aligns with the prophecy and it certainly seems like something that would get our father’s heart pumping faster."
    c "Isso a linha com a profecia, e realmente parece algo que deixaria o pai bem empolgado."

# game/episode022.rpy:541
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_868d79c5:

    # c "It aligns with the prophecy and it certainly seems like something that would get my father’s heart pumping faster."
    c "Isso a linha com a profecia, e realmente parece algo que deixaria o meu pai bem empolgado."

# game/episode022.rpy:543
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_8ffe2127:

    # e "What do you think their endgame is?"
    e "O que você acha que é o objetivo final deles?"

# game/episode022.rpy:544
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_46e2c341:

    # c "I think they all want to harness the power stored in the genetic databanks of the Shixses in some way."
    c "Acho que todo mundo quer o poder guardado nos bancos de dados genéticos Shixses."

# game/episode022.rpy:545
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_784937bc:

    # c "The Confessor likely wants to expand the influence of his cult."
    c "O Confessor provavelmente quer expandir a influência do culto."

# game/episode022.rpy:546
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_aa2afdca:

    # c "Vess told us that he resorts to stage tricks to fool his audience into thinking he has real powers."
    c "A Vess disse que ele usa truques de mágica para fazer o público achar que ele tem poderes de verdade."

# game/episode022.rpy:547
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_b3a4c19a:

    # c "The information from the Shixses would at the very least grant him some of those powers, maybe even more than that."
    c "Essa informação das Shixses daria pelo menos alguns desses poderes a ele, talvez até mais."

# game/episode022.rpy:548
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_88f1de50:

    # c "I’m not sure what Erylin’s deal is, she probably just wants to stick to someone powerful."
    c "Não sei exatamente o que a Erylin quer, provavelmente só quer ficar perto de alguém poderoso."

# game/episode022.rpy:549
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_55fcf895:

    # c "She’s a schemer, so I guess she’ll choose the side that benefits her most."
    c "Ela é oportunista, então vai escolher o lado que mais beneficia ela."

# game/episode022.rpy:551
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_f07ed0a4:

    # e "And the Confessor is on that side."
    e "E o Confessor se encontra nesse lado."

# game/episode022.rpy:552
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_012f9024:

    # c "For now at least."
    c "Pelo menos agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:553
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_3254c560:

    # c "As for the Bloodhound, Kvi, I don’t know exactly what her game is."
    c "E quanto essa tal de Cão de Caça, a Kvi, não sei exatamente o que ela quer."

# game/episode022.rpy:554
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_960eae5d:

    # c "She seems to relish in the cruelty of her job, that’s for sure."
    c "Parece que ela gosta da crueldade do que faz, isso é certeza."

# game/episode022.rpy:555
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_d64c40a1:

    # c "But ultimately she’s still an employee of the Department of Justice, not of the Sovereignty council, nor the Navy."
    c "Mas no final ainda é empregada do Departamento de Justiça, não do Conselho da Soberania, nem da Marinha."

# game/episode022.rpy:557
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_7d475b98:

    # c "So either she’s still spying on our dad, playing the long game, or acting as a free agent."
    c "Então ou ela ainda está espiando o pai, esperando a hora certa, ou agindo por conta própria."

# game/episode022.rpy:559
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_90201c41:

    # c "So either she’s still spying on my dad, playing the long game, or acting as a free agent."
    c "Então ou ela ainda está espiando o meu pai, esperando a hora certa, ou agindo por conta própria."

# game/episode022.rpy:560
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_9c416c78:

    # e "From what little interaction I’ve had with her, she sure seems slippery."
    e "Pelo pouco que a gente interagiu, ela parece bem ardilosa."

# game/episode022.rpy:562
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_bddd0fc2:

    # c "As for our father, it’s pretty clear he’s become even more drunk on power and influence."
    c "Quanto ao pai, é bem óbvio que ele ficou mais intoxicado pelo poder e influência."

# game/episode022.rpy:564
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_b9563f83:

    # c "As for my father, it’s pretty clear he’s become even more drunk on power and influence."
    c "Quanto ao meu pai, é bem óbvio que ele ficou mais intoxicado pelo poder e influência."

# game/episode022.rpy:565
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_d311adb6:

    # c "I’m very sure he’s not pursuing the prophecy for the expansion of the Sovereignty’s sphere of influence, or consolidating its power."
    c "Certeza que ele não está seguindo a profecia para expandir a influência da Soberania, nem consolidar o poder dela."

# game/episode022.rpy:566
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_b0467003:

    # c "He’s realized something about the prophecy, something that will gain the definitive upper hand or make him even more rich."
    c "Ele viu alguma coisa na profecia, algo que vai dar uma vantagem definitiva, ou deixar ele ainda mais rico."

# game/episode022.rpy:567
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_cfaa9787:

    # c "So I guess transforming yourself into some superhuman with ancient alien tech soaked in innocent blood fits right up his alley."
    c "Então acho que se transformar num super humano com tecnologia alienígena anciã banhada no sangue de inocentes combina certinho com ele."

# game/episode022.rpy:569
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_f05bb2d2:

    # e "Money and power..."
    e "Dinheiro e influência..."

# game/episode022.rpy:570
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_dabb18fb:

    # e "It’s sad really."
    e "Que triste."

# game/episode022.rpy:571
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_4c243849:

    # c "It certainly is, if it wasn’t so evil as well."
    c "É sim, se não fosse tão maligno também."

# game/episode022.rpy:573
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_600c6235:

    # e "Do you think he’s beyond redemption?"
    e "Você acha que não tem como redimir ele?"

# game/episode022.rpy:574
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_058dd7b5_1:

    # c "Yes, I think so."
    c "Acho."

# game/episode022.rpy:575
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_ae41ee48:

    # c "We don’t know half of what he did to consolidate his grip on the Sovereignty council, but the parts we know about are pretty damning."
    c "Não sabemos nem da metade do que ele fez para consolidar o controle del sobre o conselho da Soberania, mas mas o que a gente já conhece é bem comprometedor."

# game/episode022.rpy:576
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_ad874130:

    # c "I mean, he firebombed a planet just to get access to a monument."
    c "Tipo, ele bombardeou um planeta só para chegar num monumento."

# game/episode022.rpy:578
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_9e894abe:

    # e "All the more reason to obliterate this place."
    e "Mais motivos para acabar com esse lugar."

# game/episode022.rpy:579
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_23e0a2c8:

    # c "I couldn’t agree more."
    c "Concordo plenamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:581
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_eefa933f:

    # c "And you’re feeling good otherwise?"
    c "Mas tirando isso, tudo bem com você?"

# game/episode022.rpy:583
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_88ed5cd2:

    # e "Yes, otherwise I’m feeling great."
    e "Sim, tirando isso tudo bem."

# game/episode022.rpy:584
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_5dbc1644:

    # e "It’s weird at times, the idea of something growing inside me."
    e "Às vezes eu acho estranho, pensar que tem uma vida crescendo dentro de mim."

# game/episode022.rpy:585
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_3efbf856:

    # c "Exciting too!"
    c "E empolgante!"

# game/episode022.rpy:586
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_01c40558:

    # e "It sure is!"
    e "Com certeza!"

# game/episode022.rpy:587
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_8d1369cd:

    # c "No morning sickness?"
    c "Está sem enjoo matinal?"

# game/episode022.rpy:588
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_5d28a474:

    # e "Thankfully no."
    e "Ainda bem que não."

# game/episode022.rpy:593
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_6105a8c0:

    # e "There’s something else though."
    e "Mas tem mais uma coisa."

# game/episode022.rpy:595
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_327fe809:

    # e "It’s a little embarrassing."
    e "Dá um pouquinho de vergonha."

# game/episode022.rpy:596
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_6e6ce20e:

    # c "Oh?"
    c "Ah é?"

# game/episode022.rpy:597
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_b6f24c83:

    # e "I feel amped up most of the time."
    e "Na maior parte do tempo eu fico a mil."

# game/episode022.rpy:598
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_ba2a27a9:

    # c "Amped up?"
    c "A mil?"

# game/episode022.rpy:599
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_6ddf9fee:

    # e "Well...{w} You know...{w} Horny."
    e "Bem...{w} Tipo...{w} Com tesão."

# game/episode022.rpy:600
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_46099848:

    # c "I’m not sure I see the problem."
    c "Não sei qual é o problema."

# game/episode022.rpy:601
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_60fede28:

    # e "I’m sure you don’t."
    e "Imagino que não."

# game/episode022.rpy:603
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_d6f2ee12:

    # e "But here I am pulling cables from a wall and getting wet because I can’t stop thinking about you."
    e "Mas aqui estou eu puxando o cabo da parede, toda encharcada porque não consigo parar de pensar em você."

# game/episode022.rpy:604
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_e42f62af:

    # c "Well, if you put it that way, I think we should do something about that."
    c "Bom, sendo assim, acho que a gente pode dar um jeito nisso."

# game/episode022.rpy:605
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_79ad4c0c:

    # c "Come by my quarters once you’re done."
    c "Dá uma passada no meu quarto quando terminar."

# game/episode022.rpy:607
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_4527df9f:

    # e "Mmmm, I can’t wait."
    e "Mmmm, mal posso esperar."

# game/episode022.rpy:608
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_168792e7:

    # c "See you soon."
    c "Até daqui a pouco."

# game/episode022.rpy:614
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_7bb22f9a:

    # c "Keep ripping out those cables with gusto then, sis!"
    c "Então continua arrancando esses cabos com vontade, maninha!"

# game/episode022.rpy:616
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_a14d6d1f:

    # c "Keep ripping out those cables with gusto then!"
    c "Então continua arrancando esses cabos com vontade!"

# game/episode022.rpy:617
translate portuguese ep022_eva_talk_cc107a7c:

    # e "I sure will."
    e "Vou sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:622
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_a28cf302:

    # e "[p_name_short], could we have a word about something?"
    e "[p_name_short], será que a gente pode conversar?"

# game/episode022.rpy:623
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_84d9b8e4:

    # "The sudden change in tone took me by surprise."
    "A mudança repentina do tom me pegou de surpresa."

# game/episode022.rpy:624
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_d40bb89c:

    # "Eva looked very serious."
    "Eva estava bem séria."

# game/episode022.rpy:625
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_7b7a5678:

    # c "Yes, of course."
    c "Sim, claro."

# game/episode022.rpy:626
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_861588b9:

    # e "I thought it would be a good time to be honest with each other."
    e "Achei que seria uma boa hora para ser honestos um com o outro."

# game/episode022.rpy:628
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_9cb01624:

    # e "Especially with the baby on the way."
    e "Ainda mais com um bebê a caminho."

# game/episode022.rpy:629
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_f65ab8ef:

    # "I dreaded the words that were sure to come next."
    "Eu estava com medo das palavras que estavam por vir."

# game/episode022.rpy:631
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_7442c1e5:

    # e "I hope you don’t think I’m stupid, [p_name_short]."
    e "Espero que não ache que eu sou burra, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode022.rpy:632
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_d5258518:

    # c "No, of course not, I-"
    c "Não, claro que não, eu-"

# game/episode022.rpy:634
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_e6191e15:

    # e "Please, let me finish."
    e "Deixa eu terminar, por favor."

# game/episode022.rpy:635
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_5a23a4cc:

    # e "I know I’m not the only woman you love."
    e "Eu sei que não sou a única mulher que você ama."

# game/episode022.rpy:636
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_8e8a517f:

    # e "I know there are others."
    e "Eu sei que tem outras."

# game/episode022.rpy:637
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_1d87a6de:

    # e "What I don’t understand is why you haven’t told me."
    e "O que eu não entendo é por que você não me contou."

# game/episode022.rpy:638
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_a2c1b232:

    # c "There was never a right time."
    c "Nunca parecia ser a hora certa."

# game/episode022.rpy:640
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_9434ce8e:

    # e "Sorry, [p_name_short], but that’s just bullshit."
    e "[p_name_short], me desculpa, mas isso é pura conversa fiada."

# game/episode022.rpy:642
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_07127b55:

    # e "I’m pregnant with our child and you didn’t think it would be a good time to tell me then?"
    e "Eu estou grávida de você, e não achou que era uma boa hora de me contar?"

# game/episode022.rpy:643
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_e1dedcd5:

    # c "I’m sorry, Eva, I should have told you earlier."
    c "Desculpa, Eva. Eu devia ter te contado antes."

# game/episode022.rpy:644
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_68486c74:

    # c "I was scared I’d lose you if I told you the truth."
    c "Fiquei com medo de te perder se falasse a verdade."

# game/episode022.rpy:646
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_38e4c48c:

    # e "Lying to me could have just as easily made me break up with you."
    e "Eu poderia terminar com você do mesmo jeito com essa mentira."

# game/episode022.rpy:647
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_126adf8c:

    # e "It could still."
    e "Ainda posso, até."

# game/episode022.rpy:648
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_24366554:

    # c "I understand."
    c "Eu entendo."

# game/episode022.rpy:649
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_642c6789:

    # c "You probably don’t want to hear any justifications for my behavior, so I just wanted to say again that I’m sorry."
    c "Duvido que você vá querer ouvir justificativas do meu comportamento, então queria me desculpar de novo."

# game/episode022.rpy:650
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_d89434a8:

    # c "And that I won’t lie to you ever again."
    c "E que nunca mas vou mentir para você."

# game/episode022.rpy:651
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_57a64a64:

    # c "If you don’t want anything to do with me anymore, I’d understand of course."
    c "Claro, eu entendo se não quiser mais nada comigo."

# game/episode022.rpy:653
translate portuguese ep022_eva_confession_af63aad6:

    # c "But I’d hate for you to bear the responsibility of your pregnancy alone."
    c "Mas odiaria se você ficasse com a responsabilidade da gravidez sozinha."

