# game/episode022.rpy:847
translate portuguese ep022_lilly_talk_79dd7a6e:

    # c "I’m sure it’s going to be a difficult conversation, but we’ll find a way."
    c "Provavelmente vai ser uma conversa difícil, mas vamos dar um jeito."

# game/episode022.rpy:848
translate portuguese ep022_lilly_talk_b5544095:

    # c "Let’s have this moment together for now, shall we?"
    c "Por enquanto vamos aproveitar o momento, tá?"

# game/episode022.rpy:849
translate portuguese ep022_lilly_talk_c8f2ad0d:

    # l "I’d like that very much."
    l "Adoraria."

# game/episode022.rpy:852
translate portuguese ep022_lilly_talk_5dfefbc7:

    # "We lay together on the bed and I took my sister into my arms."
    "Nós estamos juntos na cama, e eu abracei a minha irmã."

# game/episode022.rpy:854
translate portuguese ep022_lilly_talk_dc0592ba:

    # "We lay together on the bed and I took my girlfriend into my arms."
    "Nós estamos juntos na cama, e eu abracei a minha namorada."

# game/episode022.rpy:855
translate portuguese ep022_lilly_talk_3016ab9d:

    # "Stroking her soft skin, we enjoyed each other’s nearness and revelled in our happiness until duty called again and we had to go our separate ways."
    "Eu acariciei sua pele macia e ficamos bem juntinhos, aproveitando a nossa felicidade até o dever chamar termos que nos separar."

# game/episode022.rpy:863
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_a9d2b982:

    # "I found my mother poring over several books and her tablet."
    "Eu vi minha mãe lendo vários livros e o tablet."

# game/episode022.rpy:865
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_fbc5910e:

    # "I found Nadya poring over several books and her tablet."
    "Eu vi a Nadya lendo vários livros e o tablet."

# game/episode022.rpy:866
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_5690bc5c:

    # c "It’s like you’re always reading when I meet you."
    c "Parece que sempre que eu te vejo, você está lendo alguma coisa."

# game/episode022.rpy:868
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_4706699c:

    # na "I do other stuff as well."
    na "Também faço outras coisas."

# game/episode022.rpy:869
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_57b195d4:

    # c "Sleep, eat, read, repeat?"
    c "Dorme, come, lê, repete tudo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:872
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_6ec3df01:

    # na "Come now, I don’t hear you complain when I warm your bed at night."
    na "Ei, não vejo você reclamando quando esquento a sua cama de noite."

# game/episode022.rpy:873
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_feed6cdd:

    # c "Good point."
    c "Tem razão."

# game/episode022.rpy:875
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_adb58572:

    # na "Well, if you put it that way..."
    na "Bem, falando desse jeito..."

# game/episode022.rpy:876
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_08f57b00:

    # c "I was wondering if I could pick your brain a little further about those Shixses."
    c "Queria saber se posso falar com você sobre as Shixses."

# game/episode022.rpy:878
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_f712a543:

    # na "Of course."
    na "Claro."

# game/episode022.rpy:879
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_d5cc8c95:

    # na "I don’t know if I’ll be of much help, there’s so little known about them."
    na "Não sei se vou conseguir ajudar muito, quase não se sabe nada sobre elas."

# game/episode022.rpy:880
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_0294b670:

    # na "In fact, everything I have here on the table are all the texts that directly make mention of them."
    na "Aliás, aqui na mesa eu só tenho textos que mal falam nelas."

# game/episode022.rpy:881
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_ae651f5b:

    # c "That’s still an impressive amount of books."
    c "Mas é um número impressionante de livros."

# game/episode022.rpy:882
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_2e49afa5:

    # na "Don’t let that fool you."
    na "Não se engane."

# game/episode022.rpy:883
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_3e0ecdf5:

    # na "Most of those text only reference the Shixses in one sentence and not even by name."
    na "A maioria só faz referência às Shixses numa linha só, e nem mencionam por nome."

# game/episode022.rpy:884
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_158131f7:

    # c "They’re that obscure, are they?"
    c "São tão obscuras assim?"

# game/episode022.rpy:885
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_b70432c3:

    # na "Yes."
    na "Sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:886
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_dfcece00:

    # c "Weird, considering the impact they seem to have had on the universe."
    c "Estranho, considerando o impacto que elas têm no universo."

# game/episode022.rpy:888
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_593af4c5:

    # na "Yes, it almost seems like there was an attempt to scrub them from history."
    na "Sim, parece até que tentaram apagar a existência delas da história."

# game/episode022.rpy:889
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_4238c1a1:

    # c "I can imagine why."
    c "Imagino o motivo."

# game/episode022.rpy:890
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_74de3eff:

    # na "The name of their homeworld isn’t mentioned anywhere, only that they were a ruthless and needlessly cruel species, who only ventured out of their system to capture hapless victims."
    na "O nome do planeta delas não mencionado em lugar algum, só que eram uma espécie cruel demais, que só saia de seu sistema para raptar vítimas inocentes."

# game/episode022.rpy:891
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_d01d8ab0:

    # c "Nothing about their genetic experiments or their forced extinction?"
    c "Nada sobre os experimentos genéticos ou extinção forçada?"

# game/episode022.rpy:893
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_346484c0:

    # na "Nope."
    na "Nada."

# game/episode022.rpy:894
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_4d5fd618:

    # na "There are some details about a coalition that rose up to them, but nothing about the genocide."
    na "Tem uns detalhes sobre um grupo que enfrentou elas, mas nada sobre o genocídio."

# game/episode022.rpy:895
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_764201bf:

    # c "That sure sounds like a cover up."
    c "Isso me parece acobertamento."

# game/episode022.rpy:896
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_41d176b4:

    # na "It does."
    na "Parece."

# game/episode022.rpy:897
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_f09f179e:

    # na "I guess the Shixses foresaw their own obscuration from history, hence the creation of the prophecy."
    na "Acho que as Shixes previram que seriam apagadas da história, por isso fizeram a profecia."

# game/episode022.rpy:898
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_904e8bc0:

    # c "Nothing like a little quasi religious mumbo jumbo to fan the flames of obsession."
    c "Nada melhor que besteira semi-religiosa para atiçar as chamas da obsessão."

# game/episode022.rpy:900
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_0021e3f6:

    # na "Yes, it was a clever move on their part."
    na "Sim, foi esperto da parte delas."

# game/episode022.rpy:901
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_ce5bd367:

    # na "They made sure that throughout the many years since their destruction, the prophecy still lingered in the minds of people, even if the record of the Shixses own existence barely withstood the ravages of time."
    na "Elas garantiram que tantos anos depois da sua destruição, a profecia ainda permanecia na mente das pessoas, mesmo que todos os registros da própria existência das Shixses mal resistiu todos os efeitos do tempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:902
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_1f56871e:

    # c "Do you think my father is one of those people?"
    c "Acha que o meu pai é uma dessas pessoas?"

# game/episode022.rpy:904
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_73ac9f3d:

    # na "He sure is now."
    na "Com certeza é agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:906
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_0c470c96:

    # c "I meant before, when he was with you, I mean."
    c "Digo, antes de ele estar com você."

# game/episode022.rpy:907
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_6d8feecf:

    # na "I’ve thought about it so much, even after I confessed everything back on Kepler."
    na "Pensei bastante nisso, mesmo depois de ter confessado tudo lá em Kepler."

# game/episode022.rpy:909
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_f704e7e7:

    # na "I told you he went away to train at a trade conglomerate and came back changed."
    na "Eu te disse que ele foi treinar num conglomerado de comércio e voltou mudado."

# game/episode022.rpy:910
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_1d1715c8:

    # na "He became even more ambitious and obsessed with his legacy."
    na "Ele ficou ainda mais ambicioso e obcecado com o próprio legado."

# game/episode022.rpy:911
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_e5b5e0ab:

    # na "I think his tenure at that conglomerate is also when he was first exposed to the contents of the prophecy."
    na "Acho que a estadia nesse conglomerado foi o que pois ele aos detalhes dessa profecia."

# game/episode022.rpy:912
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_1476c90c:

    # na "The conglomerate wanted a full profile of its interns, so before Agust went away, there were all kinds of physical tests and medical examinations."
    na "Conglomerado queria um perfil completo de seus estagiários. Aí antes do Agust ir embora, fizeram vários tipos de testes físicos exames médicos."

# game/episode022.rpy:913
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_3d67b7c3:

    # na "Maybe some disciple took a look at his genetic profile and pulled him into the conspiracy."
    na "Talvez um dos discípulos tenha visto o perfil genético dele e jogou ele nessa conspiração."

# game/episode022.rpy:914
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_b94ad783:

    # na "After it turned out that Yve couldn’t conceive, he came back to me."
    na "Quando ficou claro que a Yve não podia ter filhos, ele voltou para mim."

# game/episode022.rpy:915
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_e2990f5e:

    # na "I realize now that it was all an act, in order for me to conceive the children he desired."
    na "Agora eu vejo que era só fingimento, para me convencer a ter os filhos que ele queria."

# game/episode022.rpy:916
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_e2ad6975:

    # na "He was obsessed with the medical details surrounding your birth and your sister’s."
    na "Ele estava obcecado nos detalhes médicos do seu nascimento e das suas irmãs."

# game/episode022.rpy:917
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_847a7301:

    # na "The amount of tests that he demanded to be run even confounded the doctors who delivered you."
    na "O monte de testes que ele mandou fazer confundiu até os médicos que fizeram o seu parto."

# game/episode022.rpy:918
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_b1208bba:

    # na "What those test showed him must have satisfied Agust, because his interest waned after that."
    na "Agust deve ter ficado satisfeito com os resultados, porque ele perdeu interesse depois."

# game/episode022.rpy:919
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_f78b0707:

    # c "Until now."
    c "Até agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:921
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_7ff15310:

    # na "Yes, until now."
    na "Sim, até agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:923
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_1f19a87f:

    # c "I meant before, back on Tuolovi."
    c "Digo antes, lá em Tuolovi."

# game/episode022.rpy:925
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_91726fa1:

    # na "I’ve thought about it so much, even after I told you about his attempted rape and his threats concerning Aven’s mother."
    na "Eu pensei tanto nisso, mesmo depois que te contei da tentativa de estupro dele, e as ameaças com a mãe da Aven."

# game/episode022.rpy:926
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_4ee4a694:

    # c "That he might have murdered her or have her killed?"
    c "Que ele poderia ter ou matado ou mandado matar ela?"

# game/episode022.rpy:927
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_b70432c3_1:

    # na "Yes."
    na "Sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:928
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_fe9bad89:

    # na "Agust sees people as tools, that shouldn’t come as a surprise."
    na "O Agust vê as pessoas como ferramentas, então não é surpresa."

# game/episode022.rpy:929
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_cfcdc447:

    # na "Knowing what we know now, I don’t think it’s a coincidence Aven, Lilly and Eva were all living on the Valenmann de Lonval estate."
    na "Sabendo o que sabemos agora, acho que não é nem coincidência que a Aven, Lilly e Eva estavam todas morando na residência Valenmann de Lonval."

# game/episode022.rpy:930
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_e4e92ebe:

    # c "What, because he secretly sired Aven, Lilly and Eva?"
    c "O que, porque ele teve Aven, Lilly e Eva em segredo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:931
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_4022bd77:

    # c "Because that would-"
    c "Porque isso-"

# game/episode022.rpy:932
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_2361aa7b:

    # na "No, no, I don’t mean it like that."
    na "Não, não quis dizer isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:933
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_e3cc94e1:

    # na "Aven was already born when her mother came to work for Agust."
    na "A Aven já tinha nascido quando a mãe dela foi trabalhar para o Agust."

# game/episode022.rpy:934
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_fff4b69e:

    # na "And the mothers of Lilly and Eva were already pregnant before they even met him."
    na "E as mães da Lilly e Eva já estavam grávidas antes de conhecerem ele."

# game/episode022.rpy:935
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_58887dfe:

    # na "So he isn’t their father, but I think the hiring of them all was no accident."
    na "Então ele não é o pai delas, mas acho que contratar elas não foi por acaso."

# game/episode022.rpy:936
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_a2e55587:

    # na "Agust insisted on full medical tests for them, blood work, genetic mapping, the works."
    na "Agust insistiu em fazer testes completos nelas. Testes sanguíneos, mapeamento genético, tudo."

# game/episode022.rpy:937
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_55cc7427:

    # na "The amount of tests even confounded the doctors who were requested to carry them out."
    na "Aquele monte de testes confundiu até os médicos que os fizeram."

# game/episode022.rpy:938
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_1b1db747:

    # na "When Lilly and Eva were born the same batch of tests was run on them, all under the guise of making sure the babies were healthy and got the best possible care."
    na "Quando a Lilly e Eva nasceram, fizeram os mesmos testes nelas, tudo sob a desculpa de garantir que os bebês estavam saudáveis, e que teriam o melhor cuidado possível."

# game/episode022.rpy:939
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_f11586f7:

    # c "Yes, a loving and caring employer, that’s my father to a tee."
    c "Sim, um chefe muito carinhoso, esse é o meu pai."

# game/episode022.rpy:940
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_84ceb9d7:

    # c "So you’re saying he was testing my friends for something?"
    c "Então quer dizer que ele estava procurando alguma coisa nas minhas amigas?"

# game/episode022.rpy:942
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_2c249e55:

    # na "I think he was."
    na "Acho que sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:943
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_b1208bba_1:

    # na "What those test showed him must have satisfied Agust, because his interest waned after that."
    na "Agust deve ter ficado satisfeito com os resultados, porque ele perdeu interesse depois."

# game/episode022.rpy:944
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_f78b0707_1:

    # c "Until now."
    c "Até agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:945
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_7ff15310_1:

    # na "Yes, until now."
    na "Sim, até agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:946
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_20a85ab9:

    # c "So he knew about the prophecy when we were all little?"
    c "Então ele sabia da profecia quando a gente era criança?"

# game/episode022.rpy:947
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_87aad454:

    # na "I think so, yes."
    na "Acredito que sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:948
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_3d578b66:

    # na "I’m not sure when it started, but he travelled a lot in his younger years and he apprenticed at some big trade conglomerate."
    na "Não sei quando foi que começou, mas ele viajou muito quando era jovem. Estagiou num conglomerado grande de comércio."

# game/episode022.rpy:949
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_79dfe61e:

    # na "From what I know of these conglomerates, is that they attract all kinds of people."
    na "E pelo que eu conheço desses conglomerados, eles atraem todo tipo de pessoa."

# game/episode022.rpy:950
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_bb7fee4a:

    # c "Including disciples of ancient prophecies with a knack for recruiting."
    c "Incluindo seguidores de profecias anciãs com talento para recrutar. "

# game/episode022.rpy:951
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_9a84f6ea:

    # na "I suspect so."
    na "Espero que sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:953
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_a952025e:

    # na "He must have been initiated at a young age and his subsequent actions have all been influenced by it."
    na "Ele deve ter começado bem jovem, e a partir daí todas as suas ações devem ter sido influenciadas por isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:954
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_d8eba83f:

    # na "As I said, Agust regards people as tools."
    na "Como eu disse, Agust vê as pessoas como ferramentas."

# game/episode022.rpy:955
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_84ca1574:

    # c "And here I thought I couldn’t hate him more."
    c "E eu aqui achando que não tinha como odiar ele ainda mais."

# game/episode022.rpy:957
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_612f16ef:

    # na "Yes, the Agust of my youth has long gone."
    na "Sim, o Agust da minha juventude se foi faz tempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:958
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_13005041:

    # na "And it’s imperative that he doesn’t get his hands on the technology in that temple."
    na "E é muito importante que ele não consiga pegar a tecnologia do templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:960
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_ad8d1479:

    # na "It’s imperative that he doesn’t get his hands on the technology in that temple."
    na "É muito importante que ele não consiga pegar a tecnologia do templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:962
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_5ee56570:

    # na "I mean, the people he surrounds himself are bad enough, but I think their ambitions pale in comparison to his."
    na "Digo, as pessoas com quem ele anda já são ruins, mas acho que a ambição delas não é nada comparada com a dele."

# game/episode022.rpy:963
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_5627bddc:

    # c "Noted, we’re going to scorch that temple and then move on to any other structure left on this planet."
    c "Entendi, vamos queimar aquele tempo inteiro, e fazer o mesmo com todas as estruturas desse planeta."

# game/episode022.rpy:964
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_ccb084fe:

    # na "Good."
    na "Ótimo."

# game/episode022.rpy:966
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_540270af:

    # na "I’ll see if I can find any more about the Shixses, but I wouldn’t get my hopes up."
    na "Vou ver se consigo descobrir mais sobre as Shixses, é melhor não se animar muito."

# game/episode022.rpy:967
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_c52dccfe:

    # c "Thank you anyway, for trying."
    c "Obrigado por tentar mesmo assim."

# game/episode022.rpy:970
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_fa7476a7:

    # "I left my mother to it and went back to my quarters."
    "Deixei a minha mãe e  voltei para o meu quarto."

# game/episode022.rpy:972
translate portuguese ep022_nadya_talk_587d4f4c:

    # "I left Nadya to it and went back to my quarters."
    "Deixei a Nadya e voltei para o meu quarto."

# game/episode022.rpy:979
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_fab4e9fe:

    # c "Is it safe to come in?"
    c "Posso entrar?"

# game/episode022.rpy:980
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_04ea1b6f:

    # th "Yup, nothing’s going to blow up."
    th "Aham, não tem nada explodindo."

# game/episode022.rpy:981
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_8349736e:

    # th "Not yet, anyway."
    th "Pelo menos não ainda."

# game/episode022.rpy:982
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_3d54811a:

    # c "That sounds reassuring."
    c "Isso me deixa tão tranquilo."

# game/episode022.rpy:983
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_0ba8101e:

    # c "What are you working on?"
    c "Está fazendo o quê?"

# game/episode022.rpy:985
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_d2423510:

    # th "I’m trying to set up the detonators, so that we have a good spread of explosions once we hit the button."
    th "Tentando configurar os detonadores para espalhar bem as explosões quando for detonar."

# game/episode022.rpy:986
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_d86659f8:

    # c "Do you think it will work?"
    c "Acha que vai dar certo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:987
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_f88f44f6:

    # c "I mean, considering parts of the planet were nuked without leaving as much as a scratch."
    c "Digo, considerando que partes do planeta levaram explosões nucleares sem deixar um arranhão."

# game/episode022.rpy:988
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_31bf4c79:

    # th "I’m pretty confident."
    th "Tenho bastante certeza."

# game/episode022.rpy:989
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_251f3140:

    # th "The exterior of the buildings seems to be impenetrable, as we learned in the simulation."
    th "A parte de fora dos prédios parece ser impenetrável, como vimos na simulação."

# game/episode022.rpy:990
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_070384f6:

    # th "But the interior breaks just as easily as the Bastard’s."
    th "Mas por dentro, quebra tão fácil quanto as da Bastarda."

# game/episode022.rpy:991
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_1c45be1e:

    # c "You did some test, I assume?"
    c "Então você deve ter feito algum teste?"

# game/episode022.rpy:992
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_dc11d64a:

    # th "Yes, I ran some tests and there’s no reason to think the interior is as indestructible as the outside."
    th "Sim, eu fiz uns testes e não tem motivo para achar que o interior é tão indestrutível quanto lá fora."

# game/episode022.rpy:993
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_cb8efe64:

    # c "And by tests, you mean you blew shit up?"
    c "E por testes, quer dizer que explodiu umas paradas?"

# game/episode022.rpy:995
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_c013a1dc:

    # th "That’s exactly what I mean."
    th "Exatamente o que eu quero dizer."

# game/episode022.rpy:996
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_139c6bba:

    # c "Good."
    c "Ótimo."

# game/episode022.rpy:997
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_414a6b8d:

    # c "Do you think we’ll be able to clean the entire planet?"
    c "Acha que vamos conseguir limpar o planeta inteiro?"

# game/episode022.rpy:999
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_93100c48:

    # th "Céline and Jade are mapping all the locations where buildings can be found."
    th "A Céline e a Jade estão mapeando todos os prédios localizados no planeta."

# game/episode022.rpy:1000
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_acd0ebba:

    # th "It’s slow-going, but we’re getting there."
    th "Demora, mas estamos avançando."

# game/episode022.rpy:1001
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_ec51a9cd:

    # th "Our only enemy is time in this case."
    th "O nosso único inimigo agora é o tempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1002
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_fb851412:

    # th "Because if your father is still hot on our tail and comes barging in, the fun will definitely be over."
    th "Porque se seu pai ainda está colado na gente e chegar com tudo aqui, acabou a nossa diversão."

# game/episode022.rpy:1003
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_24914cae:

    # c "Yeah, we’re in a hurry no matter what."
    c "Pois é, estamos com pressa de um jeito ou de outro."

# game/episode022.rpy:1004
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_364fc1c3:

    # c "Are we monitoring atmospheric entries?"
    c "Estamos monitorando as entradas na atmosfera?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1006
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_532664f4:

    # th "Céline says that’s impossible with all the static in the air."
    th "Céline disse que é praticamente impossível com tanta estática no ar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1007
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_15bc9498:

    # c "So we won’t know when we get unwelcome company?"
    c "Então nós vamos saber quando aparecer companhia indesejável?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1009
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_a15b8f2e:

    # th "Yes, essentially."
    th "Basicamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1010
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_1e80c200:

    # c "Nothing that can be done about that, for now."
    c "Agora não podemos fazer nada quanto a isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:1011
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_8726073a:

    # c "We need the Bastard at hand, otherwise I’d have sent a skeleton crew up to monitor the situation from the planet’s orbit."
    c "Precisamos da Bastarda prontinha, senão eu teria mandado uma equipe pequena para monitorar a situação em órbita."

# game/episode022.rpy:1012
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_246bb4c1:

    # c "Do we have enough explosive material?"
    c "Temos explosivos o suficiente?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1014
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_f04272e6:

    # th "There’s enough material to salvage in the compounds, so I think we should be fine."
    th "Dá para aproveitar bastante material nessas bases, então acho que não vai ser problema."

# game/episode022.rpy:1015
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_de5e14f8:

    # th "Setting fire to everything could work as well, but it’s not as thorough."
    th "Também dá para atear fogo em tudo, mas acho que o efeito não seria tão bom."

# game/episode022.rpy:1016
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_44cad404:

    # c "Glad to know we have at least that option."
    c "Bom saber que pelo menos tem essa opção."

# game/episode022.rpy:1017
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_b51241ea:

    # c "Well, I’ll leave you to it."
    c "Bom, vou deixar isso com você."

# game/episode022.rpy:1018
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_7a8da528:

    # c "Just don’t blow yourself up."
    c "Só não vai se explodir, tá?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1019
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_0a12eb80:

    # th "Not my first time handling explosives, [p_name_short]."
    th "[p_name_short] não é a primeira vez que mexo com explosivos."

# game/episode022.rpy:1020
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_bb78aab7:

    # c "I know."
    c "Eu sei."

# game/episode022.rpy:1024
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_5d38e919:

    # c "Still, I would hate to lose you."
    c "Mas seria horrível de perder."

# game/episode022.rpy:1027
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_3a210adb:

    # th "Hey, [p_name_short]?"
    th "Hein, [p_name_short]?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1028
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_58cd880a:

    # th "Working on this gave me a lot of time to think about our conversation earlier."
    th "Trabalhando nisso aqui me deu muito tempo para pensar na nossa conversa de antes."

# game/episode022.rpy:1031
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_4c6da10f:

    # th "About being intimate with your other conquests, I mean."
    th "Digo, sobre ser íntima com suas outras conquistas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1033
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_58338bdd:

    # th "About being intimate with your other conquest, I mean."
    th "Digo, sobre ser íntima com sua outra conquistas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1034
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_5d8c3f57:

    # th "And I’ve decided life’s too short to get hung up on things like that."
    th "Eu decidi que a vida é curta demais para ficar preocupada com esse tipo de coisa."

# game/episode022.rpy:1035
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_a7c064b4:

    # th "So I’m all in."
    th "Então eu estou dentro."

# game/episode022.rpy:1036
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_d7fdb88e:

    # c "That’s great to hear."
    c "Que maravilha."

# game/episode022.rpy:1039
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_ed639fd8:

    # th "All of the women on the crew are wonderful, so I guess it’s not much of a punishment to get involved with them."
    th "Todas as mulheres da tripulação são tão legais, então acho que não seria tão ruim me envolver com elas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1041
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_be227fd7:

    # th "She is wonderful, so I guess it’s not much of a punishment to get involved with her."
    th "Ela é tão legal, então acho que não seria tão ruim me envolver com ela."

# game/episode022.rpy:1042
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_23e0a2c8:

    # c "I couldn’t agree more."
    c "Concordo plenamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1044
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_80e27cac:

    # th "Just wanted to let you know."
    th "Só queria te avisar mesmo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1046
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_9c7e797e:

    # th "Now go, I’ve got shit to blow up."
    th "Agora se manda, tenho coisas a explodir."

# game/episode022.rpy:1047
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_73857268:

    # "Despite her curtness, Thyia smiled as she said those words."
    "Apesar do jeito seco, Thyia sorriu quando falou isso."

# game/episode022.rpy:1049
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_15c778ec:

    # "I couldn’t help but move in and kiss her."
    "Não consegui me conter e me aproximei para beijar ela."

# game/episode022.rpy:1050
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_84b9c92b:

    # c "See you around."
    c "A gente se vê."

# game/episode022.rpy:1054
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_4951f59a:

    # "I could tell she liked hearing that, so I moved in and kissed her."
    "Deu para perceber que ela gostou de ouvir isso, então me aproximei para beijar ela."

# game/episode022.rpy:1056
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_6cbc0fa6:

    # th "What was that for?"
    th "Isso foi para quê?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1057
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_edee320d:

    # c "Just for being you."
    c "Só por ser você."

# game/episode022.rpy:1059
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_aa9706f1:

    # th "Are you going all sappy on me now?"
    th "Vai ficar todo meloso agora, é?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1060
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_d592a418:

    # c "That’s just what girls playing with high-grade explosives do to me."
    c "Garotas mexendo com explosivos de alta potência fazem isso comigo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1061
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_90ce81b8:

    # c "So hot."
    c "Ui, delícia."

# game/episode022.rpy:1063
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_46163648:

    # th "I’m sure that’s it, Romeo."
    th "Aposto, Romeu."

# game/episode022.rpy:1065
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_9c7e797e_1:

    # th "Now go, I’ve got shit to blow up."
    th "Agora você manda, tenho coisas a explodir."

# game/episode022.rpy:1067
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_573a7eac:

    # c "Still, I would hate to lose our star engineer."
    c "Mas eu odiaria perder a nossa melhor engenheira."

# game/episode022.rpy:1069
translate portuguese ep022_thyia_talk_2b14c1b2:

    # th "Duly noted."
    th "Entendido."

# game/episode022.rpy:1076
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_9ae581cc:

    # "Ziv was sitting outside, overlooking the dreary landscape of Petrarch."
    "Ziv estava sentada lá fora, olhando o horizonte sombrio de Petrarch."

# game/episode022.rpy:1077
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_1a8b4274:

    # c "Enjoying the view?"
    c "Curtindo a vista?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1078
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_952c9c6e:

    # zi "There’s not much to enjoy."
    zi "Não tem muito o que curtir."

# game/episode022.rpy:1079
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_7c1c16d5:

    # zi "This place is so oppressive."
    zi "Esse lugar é tão opressor."

# game/episode022.rpy:1080
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_23e0a2c8:

    # c "I couldn’t agree more."
    c "Concordo plenamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1081
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_16799f54:

    # c "Mind if I join you for a bit?"
    c "Se importa se eu ficar um pouco com você?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1082
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_e93810a3:

    # zi "Have a seat."
    zi "Senta."

# game/episode022.rpy:1083
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_c60e3124:

    # c "So, how’s my favorite Rhenkoy?"
    c "Então, como vai a minha Rhenkoy favorita?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1085
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_5f5db703:

    # zi "Doing pretty well, even considering the surroundings."
    zi "Até que bem, considerando o ambiente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1086
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_5fd3eacf:

    # c "Yeah, Petrarch truly is a shithole."
    c "Pois é, Petrarch é uma merda."

# game/episode022.rpy:1087
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_83b4734e:

    # c "But we should be leaving soon, after we’ve blown the place up."
    c "Mas já já vamos sair, assim que a gente explodir esse lugar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1089
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_72c8a64b:

    # zi "Good, maybe then we can look forward to the future."
    zi "Ótimo, talvez aí vamos poder pensar no futuro."

# game/episode022.rpy:1090
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_a89a0d91:

    # c "That would be nice."
    c "Seria legal."

# game/episode022.rpy:1091
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_901ea94d:

    # c "I would like to spend that future with you of course, but maybe you have anything particular in mind?"
    c "Claro, eu adorei passar o futuro com você e tal, mas você tem algo específico em mente?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1093
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_c0c027bd:

    # "Ziv took my hand and squeezed it affectionately."
    "Ziv pegou minha mão e apertou com carinho."

# game/episode022.rpy:1094
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_dd68ac3b:

    # zi "Maybe that’s just enough."
    zi "Talvez isso já baste."

# game/episode022.rpy:1098
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_13251290:

    # c "Maybe."
    c "Talvez."

# game/episode022.rpy:1099
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_4306f2c1:

    # c "I was thinking though, we haven’t really talked about it, but do you know how compatible we are?"
    c "Mas eu estava pensando. A gente conversou sobre isso, mas você sabe se somos compatíveis?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1100
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_ca70c704:

    # zi "Considering the great times we’ve had so far, I’d say we’re very compatible."
    zi "Considerando toda a diversão que tivemos, eu diria que somos bem compatíveis."

# game/episode022.rpy:1101
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_2935dd2a:

    # c "No argument there, but that’s not really what I meant."
    c "Não vou discordar, mas não era disso que eu estava falando."

# game/episode022.rpy:1102
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_3b99799d:

    # c "I know it’s a long shot, but I was hoping you knew if humans and Rhenkoy are genetically compatible."
    c "Eu sei que é bem improvável, mas queria saber se você sabia se humanos e Rhenkoy são compatíveis."

# game/episode022.rpy:1104
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_4bc8f337:

    # zi "You mean in order to conceive children?"
    zi "Quer dizer para ter filhos?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1105
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_26eefe0a:

    # c "Yes."
    c "Sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:1106
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_2de3e36d:

    # c "I know it’s rare, but also that compatibility exists in a small number of species."
    c "Eu sei que é raro, mas algumas espécies são compatíveis."

# game/episode022.rpy:1107
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_51903e77:

    # c "You don’t have to answer if I’ve just involuntarily insulted you by jumping ahead a hundred sacred levels of Rhenkoy Companionship."
    c "Não precisa responder se eu acabei te insultando sem querer pulando uns cem níveis sagrados de Cortejo Rhenkoy."

# game/episode022.rpy:1109
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_4ccf4f3e:

    # zi "I think we’re well past caring about all those rules."
    zi "Acho que a gente já parou de se importar com essas regras já faz tempo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1110
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_c5c117d7:

    # c "Yes, I think so too."
    c "Também acho."

# game/episode022.rpy:1112
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_fc5762f3:

    # zi "Why are you asking about all this though?"
    zi "Mas por que você está perguntando isso?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1113
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_8fa0f0ee:

    # zi "Do you want children?"
    zi "Você quer ter filhos?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1114
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_8a29e1eb:

    # c "Yes, I do."
    c "Quero."

# game/episode022.rpy:1115
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_6e486f99:

    # c "With you, if there’s a chance."
    c "Com você, se tiver alguma chance."

# game/episode022.rpy:1116
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_ba4a77f8:

    # zi "Yes, I believe there is."
    zi "Acredito que tem."

# game/episode022.rpy:1118
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_6cf6a3fa:

    # zi "There’s a reason the Rhenkoy are so often involved in humanitarian efforts and diplomatic missions."
    zi "Tem um motivo para Rhenkoy se envolverem tanto em missões diplomáticas e humanitárias."

# game/episode022.rpy:1119
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_2a4af3fe:

    # zi "Empathy and adaptability are often cited as general characteristics of our species."
    zi "Empatia e adaptabilidade geralmente são citadas como características da nossa espécie."

# game/episode022.rpy:1120
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_f9ced2fb:

    # c "All good qualities in a future mother, I’d presume."
    c "Imagino que sejam boas numa mãe."

# game/episode022.rpy:1121
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_009cc907:

    # zi "True, but that’s not the reason why I mention it."
    zi "Verdade, mas não foi por isso que eu mencionei."

# game/episode022.rpy:1122
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_34392684:

    # zi "The adaptability goes quite far and isn’t just mental, but physical too."
    zi "A adaptabilidade é bem extensa, e não é só mental. Também é física."

# game/episode022.rpy:1123
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_7eb68e69:

    # zi "Our bodies can welcome the sperm of any species and allow it to fertilise our eggs."
    zi "Os nossos corpos aceitam o esperma de qualquer espécie, e permitem que fertilizem nossos óvulos."

# game/episode022.rpy:1124
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_855af6b4:

    # zi "It’s not something done often, but there are cases of Rhenkoy acting as surrogate mothers for other species."
    zi "Não é comum ser feito isso, mas há casos em que Rhenkoy servem de mães de aluguel para outras espécies."

# game/episode022.rpy:1125
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_98400f39:

    # c "You’re saying Rhenkoy can get pregnant by a non-Rhenkoy male by just willing it to be?"
    c "Quer dizer que as Rhenkoy pode engravidar de um não-Rhenkoy só por querer mesmo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1127
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_296c608f:

    # zi "Not exactly, but close enough."
    zi "Quase isso, não exatamente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1128
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_2d7eb514:

    # c "And is this true for any Rhenkoy?"
    c "E isso é verdade para qualquer Rhenkoy?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1130
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_543e855a:

    # zi "Yes, it is."
    zi "É sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:1131
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_4de65512:

    # c "I never knew..."
    c "Não tinha ideia..."

# game/episode022.rpy:1132
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_95f45f89:

    # zi "It’s not something we advertize widely, people with bad intentions might take notice."
    zi "Não falamos muito abertamente sobre isso, porque pessoas com más intenções podem perceber."

# game/episode022.rpy:1133
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_038fcbbc:

    # c "Yes, I can imagine."
    c "Imagino."

# game/episode022.rpy:1134
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_98d2d185:

    # c "Rhenkoy breeding farms..."
    c "Criatórios Rhenkoy..."

# game/episode022.rpy:1136
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_1e03c871:

    # "Ziv shuddered at the thought and looked deep into my eyes."
    "Ziv estremeceu com essa ideia e olhou profundamente nos meus olhos."

# game/episode022.rpy:1137
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_ab84a546:

    # zi "So, coming back to your question."
    zi "Então, voltando à sua pergunta."

# game/episode022.rpy:1139
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_c401a350:

    # zi "Yes, we are compatible. "
    zi "Sim, somos compatíveis."

# game/episode022.rpy:1140
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_80888328:

    # zi "And I feel so stupid for not bringing it up earlier."
    zi "E me sinto tão boba de ter não ter mencionado isso antes."

# game/episode022.rpy:1141
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_4e5a4202:

    # c "Why?"
    c "Por quê?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1143
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_47750868:

    # zi "Because I’d want nothing more than to have a child with you!"
    zi "Porque ter um filho com você é o que eu mais queria!"

# game/episode022.rpy:1144
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_1e43790d:

    # zi "I was too afraid to bring it up, thinking it might have scared you off."
    zi "Eu estava com tanto medo de falar, achando que você pularia fora."

# game/episode022.rpy:1145
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_cac27495:

    # c "I don’t scare that easily, Ziv, I can handle it."
    c "Eu não corro tão fácil assim, Ziv. Eu aguento."

# game/episode022.rpy:1146
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_89cb9c01:

    # zi "I’m so happy to hear you say that."
    zi "Fico tão feliz em saber disso."

# game/episode022.rpy:1147
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_58414f1e:

    # zi "Maybe there was also some leftover reticence because of my Rhenkoy beliefs about handling relationships."
    zi "Talvez eu estava hesitando por causa das minhas crenças Rhenkoy de como lidar com um relacionamento."

# game/episode022.rpy:1148
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_b63c87a3:

    # c "Yes, I do realize we’re still going at all this at breakneck speed from a Rhenkoy standpoint."
    c "Sim, eu vejo que estamos indo super rápido do ponto de vista Rhenkoy."

# game/episode022.rpy:1149
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_2e86b6f6:

    # c "But I’m so glad we had this conversation."
    c "Mas ainda bem que tivemos essa conversa."

# game/episode022.rpy:1150
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_c4fc5675:

    # c "So we’re going to try for a baby?"
    c "Então, vamos tentar ter filho?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1152
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_69390a38:

    # zi "Yes, we are."
    zi "Sim, vamos."

# game/episode022.rpy:1153
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_630ed6be:

    # c "That makes me so happy."
    c "Isso me deixa tão feliz."

# game/episode022.rpy:1154
translate portuguese ep022_ziv_talk_7b5279d3:

    # zi "Me too."
    zi "Eu também."

# game/episode022.rpy:1155
