    # "The soldier who’d remained behind was staring out over the landscape and didn’t notice Céline and Aven until they covered his mouth and stabbed him in the neck."
    "O soldado que havia ficado estava observando o ambiente e não percebeu Céline e Aven até que cobriram a boca dele e o esfaquearam no pescoço."

# game/episode022.rpy:1611
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_b5d38404:

    # "He went down quietly, which was my cue to get into action."
    "Ele caiu facinho, essa foi minha deixa para entrar em ação."

