    # "Céline nor Aven protested and began to sneak from our vantage point to the entrance of the compound."
    "Céline e Aven não reclamaram e já foram se esgueirando do nosso esconderijo até a entrada."

# game/episode022.rpy:1624
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_eb14a2a3:

    # "I brandished my knife and made some noise to draw attention to myself."
    "Eu puxei a faca e fiz barulho para chamar a atenção."

# game/episode022.rpy:1625
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_728dc737:

    # "As they turned to face my position, Aven and Céline circled round and ran up to them from behind."
    "Quando viraram para me ver, Aven e Céline deram a volta e correram para trás deles."

# game/episode022.rpy:1626
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_96787061:

    # "When I saw they were in position I revealed myself just enough to get the guard’s attention."
    "Quando vi que estava em posição, eu me revelei só o bastante para chamar a atenção dos guardas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1628
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_e9cb5bc8:

    # "Before any of them could investigate the disturbance or even level their gun at me, they were stabbed by the two women."
    "Antes que algum deles conseguisse investigar o barulho, ou mesmo apontar a arma em mim, foram esfaqueados pelas mulheres."

# game/episode022.rpy:1629
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_068d295e:

    # "We left them to bleed out near the entrance and opened the door to the compound."
    "Deixamos ele sangrando perto da entrada e abrimos as portas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1631
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_f4c63930:

    # "The corridor was deserted, so we headed inside to find out where our friends were."
    "O corredor estava deserto, então fomos entrando para descobrir onde estavam as nossas amigas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1632
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_1903dc34:

    # "It didn’t take long for us to find them, as we heard familiar voices coming out the meeting room we’d used ourselves."
    "Não demoramos para encontrá-las, ouvindo as vozes familiares vindo da sala de reuniões que tínhamos usado."

# game/episode022.rpy:1633
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_a79d0e9b:

    # "The entrance wasn’t guarded, so I sneaked toward it in order to see if everyone was accounted for."
    "A entrada não estava protegida, então fui me esgueirando até lá para ver se estava todo mundo lá."

# game/episode022.rpy:1635
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_fa5eb361:

    # "The entire crew was seated at the table, surrounded by guards, the Confessor and my father."
    "Todas estavam sentadas na mesa, cercadas por guardas, o Confessor e meu pai."

# game/episode022.rpy:1636
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_20988bb5:

    # "Eva and Lilly were spitting venom at them."
    "Eva e Lilly estavam gritando alto com eles."

# game/episode022.rpy:1637
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_9976fe7f:

    # e "If you have one decent bone in your body, you’ll let us go."
    e "Se você tivesse o mínimo de decência, soltaria a gente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1638
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_0b9cc504:

    # l "He doesn’t, Eva."
    l "Ele não tem, Eva."

# game/episode022.rpy:1639
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_a2b5986d:

    # l "He’s a psychopath, you must know that by now."
    l "É um psicopata, você já devia saber disso."

# game/episode022.rpy:1641
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_c3ff2905:

    # ag "Are these remarks supposed to hurt me, my daughters?"
    ag "Isso era para me machucar, minhas filhas?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1642
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_7f03c486:

    # l "Go fuck yourself, I’m no daughter of yours."
    l "Vai tomar no seu cu, não sou sua filha."

# game/episode022.rpy:1644
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_97462fd9:

    # ag "Are these remarks supposed to hurt me, girls?"
    ag "Isso era para me machucar, garotas?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1645
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_49671c90:

    # l "Go fuck yourself."
    l "Vai tomar no seu cu."

# game/episode022.rpy:1646
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_826f704f:

    # ag "You always had a foul mouth, didn’t you Lilly?"
    ag "Você sempre teve a boca suja, hein, Lilly?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1648
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_17002d1e:

    # ag "I always thought you should have been more involved in their upbringing, Nadya, would you just listen to those unruly children."
    ag "Eu sempre achei que você devia estar mais envolvida na criação delas, Nadya. Escuta só essas crianças malcriadas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1649
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_a8a07555:

    # na "Fuck you, Agust."
    na "Vai à merda, Agust."

# game/episode022.rpy:1651
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_2c3716f3:

    # "I got back to Céline and Aven to relay what I’d just seen."
    "Eu voltei até Céline e Aven para contar o que eu vi."

# game/episode022.rpy:1652
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_e516cbca:

    # c "Everyone is there."
    c "Está todo mundo lá."

# game/episode022.rpy:1653
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_7d9f6886:

    # c "Not a lot of soldiers though, so they must be elsewhere."
    c "Mas não tem muita soldados, devem estar em outro lugar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1654
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_1eac0185:

    # c "Can you disable the lift to the lower level, Céline?"
    c "Céline, tem como desabilitar o elevador lá para baixo?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1655
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_4fea926d:

    # ce "I think so."
    ce "Acho que sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:1657
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_d6fc1bed:

    # "We waited for her to sabotage the lift and drew our pistols when she came back."
    "Esperamos ela sabotar o elevador e puxamos as pistolas quando voltou."

# game/episode022.rpy:1659
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_309051c0:

    # ce "Done."
    ce "Pronto."

# game/episode022.rpy:1660
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_92c83e0f:

    # c "Let’s go make some noise."
    c "Já vamos chegar fazendo barulho."

# game/episode022.rpy:1662
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_986e727d:

    # "With drawn weapons we approached the entrance of the meeting room."
    "Chegamos a entrada da sala de reuniões com as armas apontadas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1663
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_aa2778e9:

    # c "Drop your weapons!"
    c "Joguem suas armas!"

# game/episode022.rpy:1664
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_717c11b5:

    # "Everyone turned toward us."
    "Todos se viraram a nós."

# game/episode022.rpy:1665
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_03fcaedf:

    # c "I said, drop your weapons!"
    c "Eu disse para jogarem as armas!"

# game/episode022.rpy:1667
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_e84642bb:

    # "Neither of the soldiers complied, so I fired on one of them."
    "Nenhum dos soldados obedeceram, então atirei em um deles."

# game/episode022.rpy:1668
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_dd613c07:

    # c "Drop them."
    c "Solta."

# game/episode022.rpy:1673
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_01999ae8:

    # "The other soldier dropped his gun as his comrade crumpled to the floor."
    "Outros soldado soltou a arma quando seu companheiro caiu no chão."

# game/episode022.rpy:1674
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_1d34bb0d:

    # "My father was smiling at me, the Confessor just stared dispassionately."
    "Meu pai estava sorrindo, e o Confessor só ficou olhando sem emoção em alguma."

# game/episode022.rpy:1676
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_bb8a401b:

    # ag "I knew you’d come."
    ag "Sabia que você viria."

# game/episode022.rpy:1677
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_fa5c0f15:

    # ag "You and I have some unfinished business."
    ag "Temos negócios inacabados."

# game/episode022.rpy:1678
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_2ee896ce:

    # ag "You see, I really wanted you to die, but instead you somehow survived being thrown into a vacuum."
    ag "Eu queria muito que você morresse, sabia. Mas de alguma forma você conseguiu sobreviver ser jogado no vácuo do espaço."

# game/episode022.rpy:1679
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_82cb511f:

    # ag "So I really want to do it right this time."
    ag "Então dessa vez eu quero fazer direito."

# game/episode022.rpy:1680
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_4ef26255:

    # c "Sorry to disappoint."
    c "Sinto muito te decepcionar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1681
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_6d8c2e7b:

    # c "Also, we seem to be holding you at gunpoint, so I don’t think that plan to kill me is going to get much headway."
    c "E até onde eu vi, estamos com armas apontadas em você, então acho que esse plano de me matar não vai dar muito certo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1682
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_d8e29e17:

    # ag "Ah, but you’re gravely mistaken on that count."
    ag "Ah, mas você está muito errado aí."

# game/episode022.rpy:1684
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_761985b6:

    # bl "Drop your weapons."
    bl "Soltem suas armas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1685
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_a1f3a0f6:

    # er "Don’t even think about it girl, drop that gun."
    er "Nem pense nisso garota, solte essa arma."

# game/episode022.rpy:1686
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_5f28eb67:

    # "The Bloodhound and Erylin had entered the compound."
    "O Cão De Caça e a Erylin entraram na sala."

# game/episode022.rpy:1688
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_92949007:

    # "With them was a the full contingent of soldiers Thim had mentioned."
    "Com elas, um monte de saudades que o Thim tinha mencionado."

# game/episode022.rpy:1690
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_5f1a414a:

    # "With them was a the full contingent of soldiers Raene had mentioned."
    "Com elas, um monte de saudades que a Raene tinha mencionado."

# game/episode022.rpy:1691
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_f3633e47:

    # "We had no choice but drop our weapons."
    "Não tivemos escolha, tivemos que soltar as armas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1693
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_0f160f88:

    # ag "Kvi has been lying in wait for you."
    ag "Kvi estava esperando vocês."

# game/episode022.rpy:1694
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_4444059a:

    # ag "You didn’t think you could breach our defences so easily, did you?"
    ag "Você não achou que conseguiria penetrar as nossas defesas estão facilmente, pensou?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1695
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_432f830a:

    # c "You truly don’t care about human lives, do you?"
    c "Você realmente não se importa com vidas humanas, né?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1697
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_64cde9c6:

    # co "Necessary sacrifices."
    co "Sacrifícios necessários."

# game/episode022.rpy:1699
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_3dcd4406:

    # ag "I didn’t kill those soldiers outside, boy, you did."
    ag "Não fui eu quem matou aqueles soldados, garoto, foi você."

# game/episode022.rpy:1700
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_286d27c0:

    # ag "Now, I think we’re all going on a little trip."
    ag "Agora, agora acho que vamos todos dar um passeiozinho."

# game/episode022.rpy:1701
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_9e3147e6:

    # ag "Reunite with the rest of your crew."
    ag "Reunir com o resto da sua tripulação."

# game/episode022.rpy:1703
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_2fdfc836:

    # l "You’ll have to find out where they are first."
    l "Você vai ter que descobrir onde estão."

# game/episode022.rpy:1704
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_7507c361:

    # ce "And we’re not talking."
    ce "E não vamos falar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1706
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_1f6ef3cc:

    # ag "You don’t have to run that pretty little mouth at all."
    ag "Você não precisa abrir essa boquinha."

# game/episode022.rpy:1707
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_64f7f84b:

    # ag "Kvi, has the tech team extracted the necessary navigational data from the rust bucket of theirs?"
    ag "Kvi, os técnicos já extraíram os dados navegacionais daquela lata velha deles?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1709
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_47b2fc49:

    # bl "They have."
    bl "Já."

# game/episode022.rpy:1710
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_b8ffa75e:

    # ag "Excellent."
    ag "Excelente."

# game/episode022.rpy:1711
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_c144b826:

    # ag "Let’s go find that temple."
    ag "Vamos encontrar esse templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1713
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_7833b8a7:

    # "We were marched at gunpoint the the exit of the compound."
    "Fomos levados sob a mira de armas até a saída da estrutura."

# game/episode022.rpy:1714
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_31c4294d:

    # "I fell in step next to Eva."
    "Eu andei ao lado da Eva."

# game/episode022.rpy:1716
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_3fc15ae0:

    # c "Are you okay?"
    c "Tudo bem?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1717
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_071b1a8e:

    # e "I am."
    e "Sim."

# game/episode022.rpy:1719
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_d353b48b:

    # e "They roughed Thim up for hiding somewhere in the base, but he’ll live."
    e "Eles bateram um pouco no Thim porque ele se escondeu na base, mas vai ficar bem."

# game/episode022.rpy:1721
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_ecb826d0:

    # e "They roughed Raene up for hiding somewhere in the base, but she’ll live."
    e "Eles bateram um pouco na Raene porque ela se escondeu na base, mas vai ficar bem."

# game/episode022.rpy:1722
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_5595e65c:

    # e "Are Thyia and Jade nearly ready?"
    e "A Thyia e a Jade já acabaram quase?"

# game/episode022.rpy:1723
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_21ec9701:

    # c "I hope so."
    c "Tomara."

# game/episode022.rpy:1725
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_d4a89f94:

    # "We were all pushed inside the transport which took of nearly immediately after the entry hatch closed."
    "Fomos jogados para dentro do transporte, que decolou imediatamente após fecharem a escotilha."

# game/episode022.rpy:1726
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_1d9e2e31:

    # "The atmosphere inside the cargo hold was muted."
    "A atmosfera dentro da baía de carga estava abafada."

# game/episode022.rpy:1727
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_051fb2c2:

    # "Soldiers kept a close eye on us and didn’t tolerate any conversation."
    "Os soldados ficaram de olho e não toleraram conversa nenhuma."

# game/episode022.rpy:1729
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_ebd529d2:

    # "When we touched down, a squadron of soldiers rushed out of the cargo hold and entered the temple."
    "Ao pousamos, uma esquadrão de soldados saiu da baía de carga e entrou no templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1730
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_8dd8d17e:

    # "Agust, the Confessor, Erylin and the Bloodhound were standing in front of the temple."
    "Agust, o Confessor, Erylin e o Cão de Caça estavam na frente do templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1731
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_5c5fe153:

    # "My father and the Confessor were obviously elated standing in the shadow of the building."
    "Meu pai e o Confessor estavam obviamente felizes de estarem na frente do prédio."

# game/episode022.rpy:1732
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_9182c117:

    # "I didn’t share their enthusiasm."
    "Eu não compartilhava do entusiasmo deles."

# game/episode022.rpy:1733
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_124b2362:

    # "The remaining soldiers pushed us out of the transport and dropped us in the vicinity of the temple entrance."
    "Os soldados que sobraram nos empurraram para fora do transporte e nos botaram na frente da entrada do templo."

# game/episode022.rpy:1735
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_cb87aca5:

    # "The doors opened and my heart sank."
    "As portas se abriram, e eu senti meu estômago revirar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1736
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_65cf050c:

    # "The squadron that was sent in to secure the building dragged both Thyia and Jade outside."
    "O esquadrão que foi enviado para vasculhar o lugar arrastou Thyia e Jade para fora."

# game/episode022.rpy:1737
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_c6effd26:

    # "One of the soldiers approached Agust and the Confessor and explained something to them."
    "Um dos soldados se aproximou de Agust e o Confessor e explicou algo para eles."

# game/episode022.rpy:1738
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_assault_54f072bb:

    # "I wished I could wipe that smug smile of my father’s face with a sledgehammer as he turned toward us."
    "Eu queria poder acabar com aquele sorriso escroto na cara do meu pai com um marreta quando ele virou para nós."

# game/episode022.rpy:1743
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_4c99815f:

    # "We continued working on the explosives, fear for the fate of our crew dictating our every move."
    "Nós continuamos armando os explosivos, o medo do que deve ter acontecido com a nossa tripulação ditando cada movimento."

# game/episode022.rpy:1744
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_1ccedfa0:

    # "No further communications were received by our devices, so we had to hope for the best."
    "Os nossos dispositivos não receberam mais comunicação, então tivemos que esperar pelo melhor."

# game/episode022.rpy:1745
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_8c2e15d7:

    # "Together with Kit, Aven and Thyia, I was working on the last remaining bombs inside the operating theater, with Jade covering the entrance corridor."
    "Eu, Kit, Aven e Thyia estávamos plantando as últimas bombas na sala de operação enquanto Jade vigiava o corredor de entrada."

# game/episode022.rpy:1746
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_72b23056:

    # "I was about to connect two wires when an unfamiliar voice barked an order."
    "Eu estava para conectar dois fios quando uma voz desconhecida deu uma ordem."

# game/episode022.rpy:1749
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_bdf72a2f:

    # man "Step away from the device now."
    man "Saia de perto do dispositivo agora."

# game/episode022.rpy:1750
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_90c2c337:

    # "I turned around and saw several soldiers coming up the stairs."
    "Eu virei e vi vários soldados subindo as escadas."

# game/episode022.rpy:1751
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_b3b3b88b:

    # "Two of them were holding Jade at gunpoint."
    "Dois estavam apontando armas para Jade."

# game/episode022.rpy:1752
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_8df7d24a:

    # man "Step away."
    man "Saia de perto."

# game/episode022.rpy:1753
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_619ee073:

    # "We all complied."
    "Todos obedecemos."

# game/episode022.rpy:1758
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_ac1ea219:

    # "The soldiers marched us out of the temple where more of them were waiting."
    "Os soldados nos levaram ao templo, onde mais estavam esperando."

# game/episode022.rpy:1759
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_ac311498:

    # "The rest of the crew was kneeling on the ground, surrounded by soldiers."
    "O resto da tripulação estava ajoelhada, cercados por soldados."

# game/episode022.rpy:1760
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_b6b634d4:

    # "Agust and the Confessor were standing a few feet away from them, joined by Erylin and the Bloodhound Kvi."
    "Agust e o Confessor estavam a poucos metros, junto de Erylin e o cão de caça Kvi."

# game/episode022.rpy:1762
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_dc507e0a:

    # "My father approached as I was forced to my knees."
    "Meu pai se aproximou enquanto me forçaram a ficar de joelhos."

# game/episode022.rpy:1763
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_746cd94e:

    # ag "There you are."
    ag "Aí está você."

# game/episode022.rpy:1764
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_fa5c0f15:

    # ag "You and I have some unfinished business."
    ag "Temos negócios inacabados."

# game/episode022.rpy:1765
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_2ee896ce:

    # ag "You see, I really wanted you to die, but instead you somehow survived being thrown into a vacuum."
    ag "Eu queria muito que você morresse, sabia. Mas de alguma forma você conseguiu sobreviver ser jogado no vácuo do espaço."

# game/episode022.rpy:1766
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_82cb511f:

    # ag "So I really want to do it right this time."
    ag "Então dessa vez eu quero fazer direito."

# game/episode022.rpy:1767
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_4ef26255:

    # c "Sorry to disappoint."
    c "Sinto muito te decepcionar."

# game/episode022.rpy:1769
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_362c7b4d:

    # ag "Thank you for leading us to Petrarch."
    ag "Obrigado por nos trazer a Petrarch."

# game/episode022.rpy:1770
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_4ee91f08:

    # ag "We probably would have found it without your help, but you’ve made it so much easier for us."
    ag "Provavelmente teríamos encontrado sem a sua ajuda, mas você facilitou tanto."

# game/episode022.rpy:1772
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_c61f9e0e:

    # ag "And you brought your sister, no less."
    ag "E você ainda trouxe sua irmã."

# game/episode022.rpy:1774
translate portuguese ep022_petrarch_standoff_5a847467:

    # ag "And you brought Eva, no less."
    ag "E você ainda trouxe a Eva."

# game/episode022.rpy:1775
